## Personal Notes

An IDS is often deployed using a **SPAN (mirror) port** or a **network TAP**, allowing it to inspect copies of network traffic without interrupting communications.

A modern Security Operations Center (SOC) commonly integrates IDS alerts into a SIEM for centralized monitoring and investigation.
